episodes.title: Secrets of the Cult School | #intrigued04
episodes.description:
Once a controversial behavior modification school, The Elan School gained notoriety for its harsh disciplinary methods and cult-like atmosphere. In this video, we dive into the disturbing history of the school, the psychological toll on its students, and the events that led to its eventual closure.
